If you choose to Stand, you will stop taking cards and wait for the dealer to finish. If you choose to Hit, you can continue to take a card, but there is also the risk of losing the game over 21 points. 4. After all players have completed their hands, the dealer reveals their hidden card. Dealers must hit until their cards total 17 or higher.
dialogue.user: You are a player in blackjack. Please beat the dealer and win the game. The dealer current card is {Spade 7}. The dealer has another hidden card. You don't know what it is. Your current cards are {Club 2,Heart 3}. You are an aggressive player and you like to hit when indecisive. Please output your action in following format: ###My action is {your action}, without any other text.
